message: "If you use this work, please cite it as below."
title: "Neo Genesis: Solo-Operator AI-Native Conglomerate"
abstract: >-
  Neo Genesis is a public, solo-operator AI-native conglomerate that
  orchestrates multiple AI agents (Claude, Codex, Gemini, Sora, Ollama)
  across a fleet of devices to operate eleven Strategic Business Units,
  conduct independent ML research (EthicaAI, WhyLab), run a
  9-layer kill-switch quantitative trading system, and publish
  citable datasets, papers, and architectural blueprints.
  This release marks the public foundation (v1.0.0) of the
  organization's source-of-truth, infrastructure, and citable assets.
